tps://www.nme.com/news/music/white-lies-to-celebrate-ritual-and-big-tv-with-intimate-uk-and-european-shows-3749497">《善意的谎言》以英国和欧洲的亲密节目来庆祝“仪式”和“大电视”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
